AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MFAO_0000054> "A measurement of the relative abundance of different isotopomers in both a parent molecule and its fragments, obtained through tandem mass spectrometry (MS/MS)")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MFAO_0000054> "tandem mass isotopomer distribution")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MFAO_0000054> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MSIO_0000184>)

