AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MFAO_0000058> "A physically or functionally distinct space within a cell (e.g., Cytosol, Mitochondria) separated by membranes.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MFAO_0000058> "compartment")
